window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A brand new ship. A brand new crew. What could possibly go wrong?</b></p> <p>When Ishmael takes a crew of academy cadets into the Toe Holds, he's unprepared for the level of trouble green hands can get into.</p> <p>Meanwhile, their academy liaison discovers what can go wrong when you learn the wrong lessons and try to teach the wrong students.</p> <p>Will they all make it back to the academy before somebody accidentally takes a short walk out the airlock without a suit?</p>"; 
